text: Serge Jean Julien Hubert (8 December 1915 - 26 May 1997) was a French sports shooter. He competed in the 50 metre pistol event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1915 births Category:1997 deaths Category:French male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of France Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Paris
